data:
Project "Make a change!" is bilateral project between two organizations -  "Everything Possible CIC" from UK and "East & West Center for Human Recourses Development" (WE Center) from Jordan.  WE Center will host volunteer from UK for 12 month period from September, 2014 until September, 2015. 

The objectives of project are: 
• To encourage intercultural dialogue between youth from UK and Jordan; 
• To develop cooperation between organizations from Middle East and Europe;
• To enhance youth mobility in UK by providing European Voluntary Service in another country; 
• To develop youth and children English skills in Palestinian refugee camp.  

Volunteer will lead English language lessons for children in Palestinian refugee camp. Volunteer will work with kids in age from 6 to 14 years old. Volunteer will use non-formal education methods in their activities with kids. 

In order to distribute results of project, volunteer will organize at least three presentations about EVS and her experience in Jordan and one presentation back in UK. Volunteer will also write blog articles what will be distributed in Jordan, UK and other partner organizations in Europe.
